#: ../en/docs/filters.md:20
msgid "## Filters Are Key-Value Pairs"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/filters.md:22
msgid "A typical filter looks like this:"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/filters.md:24
msgid ""
"```tt2\n"
"Read this page in [German]([% q.link(name=asset.name lingua='de') %]). \n"
"```"
