#: ../en/docs/multilanguage-overview.md:19
msgid "## Template Texts"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/multilanguage-overview.md:21
msgid "Common texts in templates are translated with [Template::Plugin::Gettext](https://github.com/gflohr/Template-Plugin-Gettext) an internationalization plug-in for the [Template Toolkit](http://www.template-toolkit.org/)."
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/multilanguage-overview.md:23
msgid "Take the following template snippet as an example:"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/multilanguage-overview.md:31
msgid "For an internationalized site you would write instead:"
